'From Squeak2.8alpha of 4 February 2000 [latest update: #2098] on 12 May 2000 at 10:41:28 am'!"Change Set:		055MappedCltnFix-hhDate:			10 May 2000Author:			Helge HorchAs of 2.8a2096 (non-flagship),MappedCollection>>storeString does not answer the correct source.Compiler evaluate:   (MappedCollection collection: 'CBA' map: #(3 2 1)) storeStringyields a MNU.A minor tweak is needed in MappedCollection>>storeOn:I also changed ''X storeOn: aStream'' into ''aStream store: X'  --sma"!!MappedCollection methodsFor: 'printing' stamp: 'sma 5/11/2000 19:53'!storeOn: aStream	aStream		nextPut: $(;		nextPutAll: self class name;		nextPutAll: ' collection: ';		store: domain;		nextPutAll: ' map: ';		store: map;		nextPut: $)! !